&lt;p&gt;In 1990, Mr. Jaroslav Ostrožovič started his business in Slovak part of Tokay area with 3 small barrels. After 20 years developed his business to become a stable and award-winning winery with many achievements and globally recognized medals from international competitions. Today the company grows Tokay grapes on 45 hectares of its own vineyard and uses an integrated production system.&lt;br /&gt;
Company&amp;#8217;s portfolio comprises of various wine products ranging from very special straw wine, ice wine to a wide selection of reds and whites produced from Furmint, Lipovina and Yellow Muscat.&lt;br /&gt;
Top of the production are 3-6 putnyos Tokay wines that are well known through the history by kings and queens. Tokay wines were considered the elixir of eternal youth, symbol of man power and female beauty.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Exclusively for Diners Club card members we have all the Tokay products available at special rates.&lt;br /&gt;
Just visit J&amp;amp;J Ostrožovič branded online shop and order. Included is free shipping in Slovakia.&lt;/p&gt;
